    "The study aims to make the images generated by the model consistent with human preferences by evaluating and guiding strategies.",
    "In practice, negative cuing reduces the generation of inappropriate content by avoiding specific cues, while SEGA manipulates the image generation process by adding additional cues while minimizing changes to the original image.",
